name: Gelato Runtz
description: Gelato Runtz is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Runtz and Gelato #33. Bred by Elev8, Gelato Runtz is 21% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Leafly customers tell us Gelato Runtz effects make them feel relaxed, euphoric, and tingly. Medical marijuana patients often choose Gelato Runtz when dealing with symptoms associated with pain, anxiety, and depression. The dominant terpene of this cannabis strain is limonene. Gelato Runtz features an aroma and flavor profile of vanilla, berries, and coffee.
